Package: base-files
Provides: base
Architecture: any
Depends: slind-virtual-awk, base-passwd (>= 2.0.3.4)
Essential: yes
Priority: required
Replaces: base, miscutils
Description: Slind base system miscellaneous files
 This package contains the basic filesystem hierarchy of a Slind system, and
 several important miscellaneous files, such as /etc/slind_version,
 /etc/host.conf, /etc/issue, /etc/motd, /etc/profile, /etc/nsswitch.conf,
 and others.
